name: Corbins of the Amethyst Crab
description: Hailing from the Amethyst Mines, the Corbins of the Amethyst Crab are known for cheffin up the good shit. That good good. Yeah. Now residing atop the oasis crabs of Kathoon, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
